	dprr:hasNoteText "Father of Verginia; prosecuted Ap. Claudius, the Decemvir (Liv. 3.56.1-58.6; Dion. Hal. 11.28, and 46.3; cf. Cic. Rep. 2.63; Fin. 2.66; 5.64; see above, Decemviri). See Lübker no. 2." .
